    <div class="well" id="wild-charge-hands-on" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://gizmodo.com/gadgets/gadgets/wild-charge-handson-really-does-charge-wirelessly-227215.php">Wild Charge Hands-On: Really Does Charge Wirelessly - Gizmodo</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>I hope this works &#8212; It would be great to have a &#8220;charger mat&#8221; on the table next to my front door so my wife and I can just drop our cellphone there and have it charged the next morning, rather than having to faff around with our incompatible wall warts.</p>

